      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Doesn&#39;t the two bytes required for a char object depend on the encoding? UTF8 requires 1 byte per ASCII character, 2 for BMP, 3-4 for nonBMP. Or are Char objects always 2?"
