      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
      "body" : "It depends on what the application is going to do with the numbers.  If it is going to just do textual things like finding palindromes, counting (decimal) digits, then a String is better.  If it is going to be doing arithmetic, a BigDecimal (or BigInteger) is better."
